{"tid":682813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最感人的葬禮！日本佛教寺廟為114隻機械狗送行","createTime":"2018-05-29T07:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T16:05:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed17454f9961644b434fc899fc5d541399f2db82","tid":682813,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180506/640_67a543ff5f05b1493f5fd4ea83731449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180506%2F640_67a543ff5f05b1493f5fd4ea83731449.jpg&h=744b5bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陪伴在身邊的事物未必有生命才有感情，尤其在日本的匠人傳統裡，所有物件都有靈魂，電子寵物不只是一隻機器狗，這場葬禮上，許多已白髮蒼蒼的主人們都低頭默默拭淚。<br />\n <br />\n根據日本媒體報導，上月底在日本千葉縣的光福寺，舉辦了一場特殊卻感人的葬禮，為114隻年久失修的Aibo機器狗送行，祭祀台上一隻隻機器狗並列，脖子上都掛著紙條，寫著家鄉與主人名，看著令人動容。<br />\n <br />\nSony在1999年開發出Aibo機器狗，第一代定價高達3000美元，將近9萬元台幣，在當時可說是第1款有人工智慧的家庭機器人，但因Sony經營出現問題，在7年後宣布停產，並在2014年決定停止維修服務，15萬台Aibo機器狗的「生命」就此出現了盡頭。<br />\n <br />\n雖然有前索尼技術人員組成第三方維修商A-Fun搶救Aibo，但再無新零件可替換的問題，只會隨著時間變差不會更好，被斷定「沒救了」的Aibo，甚至像器官移植一樣，在主人同意後發揮大愛被解體回收。因此維修商A-Fun在解體Aibo前舉辦集體葬禮，安慰從此失去Aibo的主人們。<br />\n <br />\n具AI人工智慧學習能力的Aibo，在長久相處下會記住主人的聲音，會跑會跳會撒嬌會生氣，主人們不只跟Aibo聊天、還會手作漂亮衣服換裝，有日本夫婦說︰「感覺自己在撫養一個孩子。」<br />\n <br />\nA-Fun的技術人員說，Aibo的主人把他看作醫生、而不是維修工程師，主人們就像在寵物醫院裡面看病一樣，會說「Aibo關節疼痛」，而不是表示機器狗關節故障。<br />\n <br />\n日本在高齡化社會、少子化、無緣社會的趨勢下，尤其無緣，失去所有緣份聯繫︰社緣、血緣、地緣，世代的孤單讓人們對機器人產生依賴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180506/1348206/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180506%2F1348206%2F&d=Z8UvfzV38QS9GCWS0GEfHZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=75d18e27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180506%2F1348206%2F&h=6a1ad798\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180506/1348206/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03267d78ecdede875d28f92ac28239f9dac5275","tid":682813,"uid":82452,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對屋企既死物有時都有呢種情感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100119f7eae9bea13a738d54917c1a46764d4c32","tid":682813,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"240565693114748fa3d7b122cfb63858fa0e0533","tid":682813,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03267d78ecdede875d28f92ac28239f9dac5275","tid":682813,"uid":82452,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對屋企既死物有時都有呢種情感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"吹氣mary?"},{"pid":"8190fa54c94762b837771fbf0fb9de4bdad00535","tid":682813,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識點講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e6ab276c96ee8c25421cfcdf06bcabed9268e2","tid":682813,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"240565693114748fa3d7b122cfb63858fa0e0533","tid":682813,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03267d78ecdede875d28f92ac28239f9dac5275","tid":682813,"uid":82452,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對屋企既死物有時都有呢種情感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"吹氣mary?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T